    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing for a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. This example utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a torque-sensing limited-slip differential, delivering precise power distribution. The chassis remains composed with a strut-tower reinforced front end and a recently inspected rear subframe. While the exterior displays a minor patina reflective of its mileage, the mechanical synchronization is excellent, featuring a recent valve shim adjustment and refreshed bushings to maintain its signature telepathic handling.",
