    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride, and it's honestly been such a dream to own. It\u2019s in great shape, super dependable, and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Everything runs just like it should, making it the perfect companion for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019ll make the next owner very happy! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take it for a spin!",
