    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential, the drivetrain offers exceptional mechanical engagement. Technical maintenance is up to date, including a professionally serviced VANOS unit and a structural inspection of the rear subframe mounting points. The chassis retains its signature balance with a communicative hydraulic steering rack and a well-sorted multi-link rear suspension. Recent valve clearances and fluid services ensure the S54\u2019s internal tolerances remain within factory specifications, making this a turn-key performance machine for the discerning driver.",
